            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Hd1e108">Rubrica 3</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De lucro et acquisitione diuitiarum</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>
      ¶ De lucro et acquisitione diuitia
      <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>rum. Rubrica. 3
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="49"/> <ref>SAlomon in prouerbiis
      <lb ed="#V" n="50"/>c. 13.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e127">Substam.
        <lb ed="#V" n="51"/>tia festinata minuetur: que autem
        <lb ed="#V" n="52"/>paulatim colligitur manu multipli
        <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>cabitur.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e137"> <ref>/ 28. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e139">Qui festinat dvitari non erit
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>innocens. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e146"> <ref>/ Idem in ecclesiast. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e148">Tempus
        <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>acquirendi et tempus perdendi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e154">
               <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>
                <ref>¶ Cronica de nugis philosophorum. c. 2 scilicet
        <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>de thalete:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e158">Thales qui primi sapiens nomi
        <lb ed="#V" n="58"/>natus est secundum quem et septem sapientes voca
        <lb ed="#V" n="59" break="no"/>ti sunt interrogatus quid difficillimum: ait
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/>acquirere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e170"> <ref>/ 6. c. scilicet de biante:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e172"> Bias vnus de
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>septem sapiententibus quesitus quid faciens
        <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>homo letatur: lucrans ait.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e180">
               <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>
                <ref>¶ Aristotelis ethincorum: li. 8. c. 8. et fi.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e184">Indigen
        <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>tie auxilium est lucrum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e190"> <ref>/ Idem retho. li. 2.
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>c. 16.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e192">Senes seruiunt lucro. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e198"> <ref>/ Idem polyti
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>corum. li. 5. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e200">De quibus. desident ciues
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>sunt lucrum et honor.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e209"> <ref>/ Lib. 6. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e211">Multi
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>magis appetunt lucrum quam honorem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e217">
               <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>
                <ref>¶ Iesus filius sirach in ecclasiast. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e221">Noli
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>anxius esse in diuitiis iniustis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e227"> <ref>/ 25. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e229">Que
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>in inuuentute tua non congregasti quomo
        <lb ed="#V" n="72" break="no"/>do inuenies in senectute tua</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e237">
               <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>
                <ref>¶ Terentius in adelphis. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e241">Pecuniam in
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>loco negligere maximum interdum est lucrum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e247">
               <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>
                <ref>¶ Oratius in epistolis: li. i. e. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e251">O ciues ciues
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>querenda pecunia primum est
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>Uirtus post nummos.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e259">
               <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>
                <ref>/ Idem in sermonibus: lib. 2. serm. 5.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="79"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e263">Dixi equidem et dico: captes astutus vbique
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>Testamenta senum: neu si vafer vnus et alter:
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/>Insidiatorem proroso fugerit hamo.
        <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>Aut spes deponas aut artem illusus omittas.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e276">
               <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>
                <ref>¶ Ouidius de arte amandi: li. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e280">Credita non
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>sulci semper cum fenore reddunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e286">
               <lb ed="#V" n="85"/>
                <ref>¶ Seneca tragediarum in hercule etheo. c. 2.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e290">Commoda cladibus
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>Magnis magna patent.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e298">
               <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>
                <ref>/ Idem epistolarum ad lucillum: li. 3. e. 3</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e302">Repsentat opes sapientia. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e308"> <ref>/ Li. 12 e. 2. et f.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e310">Ex multis paupertatibus diuitie fiunt. <!--221.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="91-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e322">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>
                <ref>¶ Lucanus: li. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e326">Paupertas fugitur: totoque
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>aceersitur orbe. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e332">
               <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>
                <ref>¶ Lex dig. t. ad legem falci. li. predia:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e336">Perpo
        <lb ed="#V" n="4"/>sterum est ante nos locupletes dici quam acqui
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>fierimus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e345"> <ref>/ Ti. de regum. iur. l. infrascriptis:</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="6"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e347">Sedm naturam est commoda cuiusque rei eum
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>sequi quem sequuntur incommoda. Iure ciuili
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>equum est neminem cum alterius detrimen
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>to vel iniuria fieri locupletiorem.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e359">
               <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>
               <ref>¶ Cassiodorus epistolarum: li. 7. e. 9.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e363">A pau
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>cis accipit qui nimium querit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-d1e369">
               <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>
                <ref>¶ Prouerb. metrice. extra ordo vel. vag.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d72872-Qd1e373">Dat ga
        <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>lienus opes: dat sanctio iustiniana.
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>Ex aliis paleas: ex istis collige grana.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
